mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.1:
Thank you for your hard work
I've been thinking about the Work you mentioned
since then.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.2:
I'd like to try
Please let me try
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.5:
Don't worry about it at all
It means you took your time and thought about it
You'll be fine at Mano's pace.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.6:
Thank you
I'll do my best
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.7:
Thank you for your hard work
Sorry for contacting you so suddenly
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.8: I'd like to tell you in person, but I'm not always able to talk to you very well, so I thought I could tell you in writing.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.11: Seeing Mano working hard gives me energy too.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.12:
Thank you.
I'm really happy to hear that.
I'll do my best to keep you healthy.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.14: I can always feel Mano's feelings.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.15:
Thank you, Mr. Producer.
I'm glad that you're joining me in my story, which always ends up being boring.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.16:
Thank you for your hard work
Do you have time tomorrow?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.17: I would like to assist you
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.18:
It's okay
Are you in a hurry? You can call me now!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.19:
It's too sudden and it's not urgent,
Tomorrow is fine.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.26: I know exactly what Hiori is thinking.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.27: I already know that it's just a short story, so there's no need to be so depressed all the time.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.29: However, I think this is something that needs to be fixed.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.30: If it doesn't work, just say no.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.32:
Hiori has spoken, right?
I'm really grateful.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.35:
It's just a matter of communication.
It's fine.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.37: Is next Sunday confirmed as Off-Time?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.38:
Okay, sure.
Unless there's something really urgent.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.40:
Yes
I support my friend's club activities!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.45: Producer, thank you for your hard work!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.46:
Hey, you're tired
What's wrong? Did something happen?
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.47: It's not like anything special happened
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.48: I feel like Producer has been busy lately.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.49: You shouldn't let busy people reply to your messages!!
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.50: No, no, these kinds of exchanges are giving me a break. I can't even make small talk.
mlMobileText_ChainTalkBodyText.52: It's the person who said it, so it must be wrong.

mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.118: As a token of our gratitude from ALSTROEMERIA, please take the smiling flower that bloomed in your heart as a souvenir
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.119:
Thank you
See you on Stage
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.122: But it's true that the present was the last box.
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.126: It's okay, there's still a lot left, Kogane
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.129: Sorry for cutting off the topic!!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.130:
You said you wanted to go sightseeing nearby when you have time.
I wonder if everyone was able to do it??
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.131: To all the fans, enjoy not only the concert, but also the sightseeing
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.134: I'd be happy if you could show me some photos.
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.135:
Let's do our best today!
Let's make it the best live ever!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.141:
No one can beat us!!
283 is the best!!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.142:
It was a live full of happiness!!
It's all thanks to all the fans who supported us!
Thank you so much! Thank you Nichika-chan too!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.143:
It was so much fun!
I wish it never ended!
See you on stage!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.144:
It was fun
I wanted to be on stage more
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.145:
I saw a lot of light.
Thank you.
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.146:
Thank you!
Toru-chan is also giving a thumbs up
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.149: Awesome, everyone, thank you so much
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.150:
Thank you very much
I really enjoyed illumination STARS
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.151: Thank you for your continued support
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.152:
Mano, Hiori, thank you!
L'antica, Houkura, Alstro, Stray, noctchill, SHHis, and CoMETIK, thank you so much!
Everyone is amazing!!!!!!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.153:
Thank you everyone
Thank you, fans
I love you♡
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.155:
I'm still lightheaded
My heart is pounding and my chest is tight!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.156:
My heart is so tight!
There were some things I couldn't do,
but it's okay to praise yourself today, right?
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.157:
It's familiar to me, and it's familiar to everyone in the audience!
The stage is in full bloom!
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.158:
Thank you
I'll never forget the cheers from the audience.
Take a good rest today.
mlMobileText_TwestaCommentBody.159:
Thank you everyone
Good night
See you again in my dreams.

mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.1:
I'm Mano Sakuragi from illumination STARS
I'll do my best to bring energy to everyone
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.2: This is Hiori Kazano from illumination STARS belonging to 283 Production
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.3:
This is Meguru Hachinomiya from 283 Pro!
Nice to meet you!
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.4:
L'antica's Tsukioka Kogane!!!
I'll do my best, so please support me!
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.6:
Shirase Sakuya / Shirase Sakuya
L'antica / L’Antica
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.7: I'm allowed to do whatever I want!
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.8:
I'm Kiriko Yuya. I've created an account.
I'm active in a unit called L'antica.
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.9: This is Kaho Komiya from HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS!
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.10:
This is Chiyoko Sonoda from HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS,
Chocolate Idol!
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.12:
I belong to 283 Production.
This is Rinze Morino from HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS.
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.14:
I'm Amana Osaki! Together with Tenka-chan and Chiyuki-san, I'm active as
ALSTROEMERIA!
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.16:
This is Kuwayama Chiyuki from ALSTROEMERIA
I'm glad you've seen this far♪
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.18:
I'm Fuyuko from Straylight♡
I'll do my best to aim for top idol♡
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.22:
I'm Koito Fukumaru from noctchill
Thank you for your help
mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.23:
It's Hinana!
Today's a good day~

mlMobileText_TwestaUserProfile.28:
This is Haruki Ikuta from 283 Production
CoMETIK

This is the official account of 283 Production

mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.1:
──Thank you for your hard work
Producer
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.2:
Oh, good job Mano
What's wrong?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.3:
I-I'm sorry...
It took me a while to get ready to go home...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.4: I think I'll be a little late to return the key to the Lesson room...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.5:
Oh, I see.
Thank you for contacting me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.6:
It's okay, it's just a little slow
There's no problem
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.7:
Um...I'll hurry as much as I can...
I'm sorry for the inconvenience...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.8:
──No, yeah
I'm glad that Mano is hurrying.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.9:
But there's no need to rush
You can come at Mano's pace.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.12:
...Thank you for your hard work, Producer
Work, finished
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.13:
Thank you for your hard work! Thank you for contacting us.
How was it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.14:
...Yes...
I feel like I did well today...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.15: Thanks to Producer for giving me a lot of advice...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.16:
Haha, that's good
I'm sorry I couldn't keep up with you
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.18: I was working while remembering Producer's words...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.19: ...I felt like you were always near me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.23: ...a big cloud shaped like a fish...──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.24:
...Hehe
It looks like he's swimming leisurely...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.26:
...I'm sorry!
I was about to take the bus──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.27: I'm really sorry, I was getting a business report, but I got off track...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.29:
I thought I should walk home
I started walking...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.30: ...And it's really fun to be able to see the same sky as Producer...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.31:
...Thank you for coming out to take a breather...
Thank you, Producer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.32:
Producer, thank you for your hard work
I've finished today's work so I'd like to report
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.33:
Good job Hiori
It's on schedule, as expected
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.34:
No,
It's all thanks to the staff that everything went off without incident.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.35:
Even though I thought I was doing my best, I was only realizing things and regretting things...
I think there's still a long way to go.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.38:
No one is perfect
Besides, being self-reflecting means you have room to grow.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.40:
Hiori still has a long way to go!
Let's reflect hard and move forward!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.41:
You've suddenly become hot-blooded...?
But... thank you
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.42:
Today's realizations and reflections,
If you don't mind, please let me directly support you
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.43:
Thank you for your hard work
The shooting has finished
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.46:
Oh, no, you're tired
Maybe your work went well today?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.47:
Um...yes,
I was complimented on my nice smile...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.49: My voice was kind of bouncy, so I thought something good must have happened.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.53: I just thought that Producer could understand that much even though it was just a voice.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.54:
──Then, I look forward to working with you tomorrow
Thank you for your hard work.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.55:
Oh, see you tomorrow...Ah, that's right
Is Hiori time still okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.56:
...? Yes, there's no problem...
Did I forget something...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.57:
No, I'm fine with work.
Let's just chat
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.58:
Hiori, you said you liked this costume, right?
That's what I was talking about with the staff today.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.59:
I've got a dress like that in mind
If you'd like, come and try it on.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.61:
No, no! I said it without permission!
I'm actually sorry.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.62:
Hiori, I was watching you seriously,
and I was wondering if you could do something with me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.64:
I'd like to hear more about that tomorrow
Thank you again.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.69: What's going on? Did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.70:
No! Nothing!
But, I wanted to tell you something right now! That's why I called!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.71:
I was wondering if you would be able to come out suddenly?
I was wondering if you were in a situation where you could come out at all.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.72:
I'm glad you came out!
So, thank you for that too!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.74:
Hehehe, yeah
Because I wanted to say 'thank you'!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.75:
…………Hey, Producer
Can I ask you something strange all of a sudden?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.77: Do you enjoy being a producer?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.78:
Of course
It's fulfilling and rewarding.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.81:
Hmm...
I always think working is fun, don't you?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.82:
Well, I thought it would be nice if the word 'fun' reached the people who watched it,
I wanted it to make them feel happy...────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.83:
But it probably won't work if it's just me
It's better if Producer, Mano, and Hiori have fun...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.84:
...I don't understand what you were trying to say!
I'm glad Producer had fun working with you! All I can say is that!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.86:
Haha, looks like it went well
I can hear it in your voice
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.88:
The appeal was perfect
The judges were also hooked!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.89:
Oh
I'm looking forward to the results
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.91: It's thanks to Producer that I was able to make my Idol.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.92:
Work hard and give back...!
Look forward to it!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.93:
...Producer, is it now?
I hope you have support.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.95: I'm going to go shopping for dinner...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.96: ...The Producer's face suddenly came to mind...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.97:
I was wondering if you ate Doganmon...
So...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.98:
Um...
So you want to hear my opinion?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.99:
...Uh, yeah...I guess I'll just ask...
I'm at work and I'm sorry...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.100:
Haha, it's fine.
You can feel free to call out to me even if it's nothing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.102:
What if...
What if I got hungry after work...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.103:
If you contact me...
I'll make something and bring it to you...tell me anything...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.106: Right now, as I was walking down the street on my way home from shopping, I saw a ball rolling.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.107: I tried to jump to avoid it, but I ended up tripping...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.109:
I just scattered the vegetables I bought on sale on the street!
It was really hard...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.111:
It's okay! I just lost my balance a little.
It hurts a bit.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.112: I-I see. That would be nice.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.113:
Well, that's fine...!
I was trying to jump like a rabbit.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.114:
You jumped better and more brilliantly...
Producer, I want you to do a self lesson!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.117:
Well, that's true...
Was there a problem?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.118:
No, I'm not.
Producer, do you know where I am now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.119:
Where is Mamimi...?
Um...I wonder where...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.120: The correct answer was in my bed at home.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.121: I'm going to take a nap now, so I'm going to brag to my busy producer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.124:
I'm starting to feel sleepy.
Producer's voice might have a soothing effect.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.125:
Well then, please do your best at
Work
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.127:
Mamimi...
What's the important thing to talk about?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.131: I will continue to do so.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.133:
Yes
It's important, so I'll report it properly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.136:
But I'm glad Mamimi said that.
She's been working hard lately.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.137: I think it's just my imagination.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.138: That's why I'll continue to do it in moderation, so please keep an eye on me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.139:
I'm tired today
I'll go home without stopping by the office.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.140:
Hey, thank you for your hard work
It must have been tough filming.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.141:
Well...
The set and costumes were quite extensive...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.143:
What do you think?
I was praised for the work.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.144: Next time, I think I'd like a job that's more relaxed and relaxed.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.146: Yes, I have a job where I get compliments just for eating sweets and lazing around.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.147: There aren't many jobs like that...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.148:
Huh?
Please do your best there, Producer
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.149:
──Hello Sakuya?
What's wrong? Did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.150:
Oh no,
I can't have that, Producer
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.151:
It's like you shouldn't call if you don't have something to do.
I'd like to be a little more playful.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.152: ──Oh, that was certainly an unsophisticated way of receiving it...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.153:
────'I'm happy to unexpectedly hear Sakuya's voice.'
...So, what do you think?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.155: If those words come from the heart, then the maiden inside me will feel like she's going to heaven...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.158: What on earth are you going to do by confusing a precious maiden?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.160: Sorry all of a sudden, Producer...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.162:
......
I don't have any particular use for this, but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.164:
...I see. But you called me.
If that's the case, I'm glad.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.166:
I just had something I wanted to ask Sakuya.
I just won a prize at the vending machine.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.167:
I chose the juice that Sakuya said was delicious.
It's a really addictive taste!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.168:
────────Ah, that's right
If you think so too, I'll be happy...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.170: Ah, I didn't make it in time...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.171:
What, what...!?
What do you mean you can't make it in time?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.173:
Actually, I was trying to send a message just now...
I accidentally tapped the wrong button...um...you call it an accidental call.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.175: I guess you wanted to cut it off before connecting
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.176:
Sorry! 
Sorry, Producer, for calling like this...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.177: No, not at all? What was it that you were trying to message me?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.178: Oh yeah, I just wanted to check────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.179: Sorry Producer, are you okay now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.180:
Oh, it's okay──Ah, wait. Can I go first?
There's something I'd like to say.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.182: I heard that Yuika received the parcel yesterday and left it on my desk.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.184: ──What the heck?! You've set yourself up a bit!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.186:
There's no need to bother...!
Just make it all thanks to the fairies.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.187:
Well,
I'm the type of person who wants to find fairies.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.188: I don't know if a grown adult would call you a fairy.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.191: ......Well, that's fine, but that's it for me. Tell me about Yuika's business──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.193:
Ah. What's going on?
After this, Audition.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.194:
Yes...before that...
I would like to talk to you for a while...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.195:
...!
Sorry, I can't come with you today
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.196:
If it's Kiriko,
just do it as usual and you'll be fine.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.197:
───Ah, that's right
Do you have the candy I gave you before you left?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.199:
You know, eating gives you strength
I want you to think you've been tricked and try eating it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.203:
Thank you for contacting me
How was it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.209:
──I wish I could have been a bird too
I could have gone to see Kiriko.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.211: It would be nice if you could come...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.222:
Thank you for your hard work!
HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS,Work completed!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.223:
Hey, thank you for your hard work
Kaho is reporting In Charge today.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.225:
I want to report to Producer!
I asked everyone!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.227:
Reporting is important
Thank you for your important role, Kaho
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.229:
Thank you,
Can I leave a message for everyone?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.232:
Mr. Producer!
Are you at the office today?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.233:
Hey, I'm here
What's up, did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.235: I want to go to the office!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.238:
Today's snack is a little extravagant
Please look forward to it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.239:
Wow!
I'll leave my school bag at home and go quickly!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.242: We played dodgeball in gym class!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.243:
Oh, how was it?
Did you win?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.245: But I was able to stay in the infield until the end.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.246:
Wow, Kaho
With the number of outfielders increasing rapidly, it will be difficult for him to stay.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.248:
I felt like I could do something today,
I tried it and I was able to do it!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.250:
I felt like I could do it...!
It was an invincible day!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.252:
Thank you for your hard work!
Producer-san, are you okay now...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.254: How many people will come to your office tomorrow...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.255: Also, I would like to know if Producer likes custard cream or chocolate cream...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.256:
Haha, even if you don't have one,
are you trying to buy me a snack?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.257: Yes! It's a local shop, but the cream puffs are really delicious...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.258:
When I see you at a department store event,
I decide not to miss it...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.259: I'm going to stop by the office tomorrow, so I thought I'd give it to everyone, but since it doesn't keep well, I'll only have enough for the people who are coming...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.260:
I see, if Chiyoko is delicious, I can only hope for it
──But first, let's have one.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.262: Don't you think it's a stupid question for me to choose chocolate or custard?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.264:
Excuse me, 1 chocolate confirmed, I'm smart!
What else should I do──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.269: ───The right to purchase limited chocolate!! I won!!!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.271: Is that the one who told me the other day...!?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.273:
I was worried about the luck of the lottery,
I thought I might not win, so I'm really happy...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.276: As long as the quantity limit allows, I would like to buy enough for myself and for everyone at the office...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.278: Sorry for not being able to come earlier...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.279:
No, it's fine. I'm sorry for asking you to call me back.
Are you okay now? Maybe you're busy with something...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.280:
It's okay!
In fact, I'm glad you called me...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.282: I was thinking of doing my homework, but it seems like I fell asleep before I knew it...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.283:
I woke up to the sound of the phone
Thank you for saving me before I couldn't take it back...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.285: ──Then I need to do it quickly so I don't run out of time for my homework.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.286:
Ah, no!
I don't appreciate your concern...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.287:
Please talk as much as you need...!
Feel free to ask us anything...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.290:
──So, the meeting is over...
I think it would be better to watch the director's past works.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.291:
I see.
I'll take a look at a few things then.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.292: ──Haha, it's amazing how Juri always finds issues and improvement ideas like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.293:
Eh... I see?
However, I may have overlooked something...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.294: I have a Producer who can give me better ideas and advice, so I'm talking like this.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.295:
Hmm, when you say that...
It makes me even more nervous...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.296:
Aha. You don't have to worry about it that much.
Well, I'm counting on you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.297: Besides, I don't need any advice────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.299:
No, it's nothing.
I'm glad to hear your voice. Thank you.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.300:
Hello? Producer
Self Lesson, now finished
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.301:
Thank you for getting in touch
You worked so hard until so late.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.302:
Yeah
I wanted it to be perfect.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.303: We can't disappoint the people who come to see us, can we?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.304: ...I'm glad I scouted Juri back then.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.306: He cares about his fans and works hard and puts in the effort.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.307: I'm sure that will be conveyed to those who watch it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.309: Also, the people who will watch it are also producers, right? Please make sure to watch it properly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.311:
Sorry...! I'll be there soon
Please wait just a little longer...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.312:
Now, when the crosswalk turns green...
Just run, it's right away...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.323:
Eh, really...
The place where Rinze is is seems to be rougher
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.324:
I can definitely hear some rumbling.
Are you okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.326:
Right now...
I can't hear you...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.328: Producer, are you working all the time?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.329:
I appreciate your hard work, but...
You should take some breaks.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.330:
...Yes, thank you
I was just thinking of taking a breather.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.334:
Oh, yeah. I just bumped into it.
Maybe it's because I've been sitting for so long, I'm unsteady on my feet...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.335:
────...Please be careful
If you do desk work all the time, your body will become dull.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.336:
I set a time to move my body...
That's right!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.337: How about turning all the chairs in your office into balance balls!?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.338:
Y-yeah...a balance ball...
I'll think about it...haha
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.339:
Your schedule is already booked well into the future...
Natsuha, is this a problem?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.342: But if you feel like you're going to have a hard time because you're too busy, please just tell me, okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.343:
Thank you
But there's really no problem...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.345: You can feel that the future is so fulfilling...don't you think so too?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.346:
────Ah, that's right
I'm looking forward to it too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.347:
You can watch Natsuha's wings fly from
closer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.348:
...hehe
I'm glad you're the producer after all.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.349: Let's continue to run together, aiming for the top!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.350: ────So, I'm sorry, but I'd like you to leave my schedule open that day.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.351:
Okay
I hope you enjoy the party.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.352:
Hehe...yeah,
but you might not have time to enjoy it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.353: There are a lot of people whose parents are taking care of them, so I think we'll just have to say hello.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.354:
Haha... I see.
Social interaction is great.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.355:
Thank you
...but I also think this is a nice thing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.356: People are connected and everyone smiles...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.357:
I just thought
this is what Producers usually do.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.358: Haha, mine isn't that flashy, but it doesn't look anything like Natsuha's gorgeous figure.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.359:
I guess so?
It looks shiny to me...hehe
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.360:
Oh, thank you for your hard work, Amana
Did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.361:
Ah, no!
It's not really an errand.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.362: I found some delicious pudding on the way home from work, so I bought some for Producer as well.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.363:
I see, thank you
I'm looking forward to it now
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.364: Hehe... By the way, how much longer is it going to be around the outside?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.365: That's right... there's still a lot to go around, so I won't be able to go back for a while.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.367:
...Okay! Don't push yourself too hard...!
I'll keep the pudding in the fridge!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.368:
Oh, I'll use that as encouragement to do my best!
See you then
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.370:
Ah, Mr. Producer...!
Sorry, I think I'll be a little late back.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.372:
Sorry! I made you worry...
It's... it's not that big of a deal...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.373: ...I went out without an umbrella, so I took shelter from the rain...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.374:
I see...that's fine...
No, it's not good. Where are you?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.376: Okay, I'll be right there, wait for me
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.377:
What!? But Mr. Producer
I heard you have a lot of plans today...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.378: Yeah, but I have enough time to pick up Amana, so don't worry too much.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.380:
Oh, Amana
I thought you had the day off today. Did something happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.382:
I accidentally pressed the call button
I tried to hang up right away, but it connected
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.383: So, I don't have anything to do...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.384:
Haha, I see
It's okay, I was just relaxing too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.385:
I-I see...
Then... can I talk to you for a bit...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.388: Well... I was baking pancakes for a snack earlier, and they turned out really well---
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.390:
Hey, what's up?
We're about to have a lesson.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.392:
Today's trainer...
He's tough...I'm a little scared...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.394:
But... if Producer...
encouraged me... maybe it would be okay...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.395:
Oh, I see...!
I wish it was over the phone---
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.396:
──Tenka can do it!
I'm rooting for you, so come on!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.399:
Mr. Producer...!
Next time... let's play a game with Tenka...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.402:
Mr. Producer...
You always seem busy...so...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.405: Thank you, I'm glad, but don't worry, I'm also taking plenty of rest.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.406:
──But, it looks like we're here.
Let's play a game together for a change of pace!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.408:
I'll lend you the controller too...
I'll lend it to you...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.420:
Excuse me...
I'm referring to the column I gave you today.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.421:
When I re-read it,
I was really curious about the details.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.422:
──Can I have just one more day
of your time?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.423:
Oh, no problem
The deadline is still a long way off
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.424: I'm really sorry, it was my selfishness...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.426: If it's released under Chiyuki's name, Chiyuki has to be satisfied with it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.428:
If Chiyuki wants to do that, I'm sure you can make it even better
Please put in as much effort as you want.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.430: Producer, please try to stretch as hard as you can!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.433:
Hehe, what do you think?
Your tension has been relieved, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.434:
Ah, thank you. My neck area feels refreshed.
I was surprised because it happened so suddenly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.436: I think you're working hard today as well.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.437: I just wanted you to relax a little bit.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.438:
Haha, thank you. It actually took the weight off my shoulders
That was good timing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.439: I'm going to make some coffee and take a break.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.440:
Hehe, then...
Coffee time, can I join you from a distance?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.441:
プロデューサーさん、連絡くださってました？
出られなくてごめんなさい……！
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.442:
ああ、こっちこそ休みなのに悪い
忙しいようなら明日でもいいけど──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.443:
いえ、もう大丈夫です
映画を観ていたので、電源を切っていて……
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.444:
どうりでなんだか楽しそうな声をしてると思った
どんな映画だったんだ？
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.445:
はい、とっても良い映画だったので、つい……
名画のリバイバル上映だったんですけど
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.446:
主演女優さんのファッションや立ち居振る舞いが
全部、可愛らしくって……！
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.447:
あ、すみません……
あんまり素敵で、ほんと、憧れちゃうなぁって……
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.448:
はは、すっかり気に入ったみたいだけど
千雪もそんな風に言われるようになるかもしれないよな
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.450:
ああ
千雪はもう憧れられる側なんだから
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.452:
Mr. Producer
I found an amazing building!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.453: There are so many cracks in the wall, there's so much ivy covering them!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.454:
Hmm... Is that so?
Is it an empty house?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.455:
I don't know
I'll have to find out...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.456:
Hey, even if the house is empty,
you can't just enter it without permission, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.458: Hmm...I'm curious to see what the ivy looks like from inside that house.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.459:
──Now that I think about it, I once went to a Western-style building covered in ivy for a location shoot.
Maybe you can see the inside as well.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.460:
Oh, really!
I want you to take me with you!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.461:
Okay, okay
Let's go together next time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.463:
...Asahi, is something wrong?
You're supposed to be at school now...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.465: I have something interesting to say!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.466:
No, you shouldn't call if you don't have anything to do
It's school.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.468:
You can wait until school is over,
Please come back then.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.469: ...Okay, I'll have an interesting story ready by then!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.470:
────Hmm!?
Well, I don't know...I'll do my best...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.473:
Too bad! The meeting took so long...!
The recording is already over, I'll be there soon────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.475:
Asahi, what's wrong?
I heard some loud noises...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.476:
...Something has started
A live performance on the street? There are some really flashy people!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.477:
Ah, Asahi! Did you go out?
I'll have to wait for you in the waiting room......
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.478:
Wow...that sounds amazing
What does the song say?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.479: Aha! I don't know, but it looks fun!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.480:
I'm interested!
I'm going to take a look!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.481:
Wait, Asahi!
Tell me where you are────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.484:
For some reason
that's how your voice sounded.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.485: It's not that big of a deal...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.486: The air conditioning was strong in the studio earlier, so I might have gotten a little cold.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.487:
Okay. It's right in front of the convenience store.
I'll buy something that's easy on my stomach.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.488: You don't have to worry about that...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.489:
──────
Ah, thank you for your hard work!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.494:
Look... at the scene just now,
you said something a little harsh, didn't you?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.495:
Hehe, what?
Did you think it was dented?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.499: But it's true that it was said in a terrible way, so I hope Fuyuko was hurt even a little.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.501:
If you need anything, call me
I'll always listen.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.503:
──────Yes, I understand
If you need anything, please chain with me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.506: Today's costume looked great on you
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.508:
Oh, yeah...
I wanted to tell you one more time
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.509:
If you ask me that much,
I don't think Fuyu is like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.510:
Oh, no...
That's what I meant
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.513:
Thank you for your hard work, Mei
Would you like to confirm something about work?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.514:
Oh, it's not like that at all~
I just wanted to talk to the producer~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.520: We all decided to have lunch together, so we connected the desks, opened the bento box, and guess what happened?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.521:
I see...
Was it empty? Or something?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.522:
Ahaha, that's a big deal~
But that's wrong~, I got my brother's name and mine's wrong~──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.523:
Hello, Producer
Is it okay now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.524:
Oh, it's okay
...you seem to be in a good mood
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.525:
Ahaha, you get it~
At the station, you found my poster~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.526:
Oh, that promotional photo I took the other day
Mei liked it and said it was a good shot.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.527: That's it! It was the first time I saw it posted, so I couldn't help but feel happy.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.528:
...That's nice, isn't it?
Isn't it amazing how much effort we put in?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.529:
Haha, Mei, right?
I'm just lending you my strength──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.531:
...That's right
It's the result of me and Mei's efforts.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.532: Hey! I passed! So let's go see it together next time!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.533:
Hello, Producer?
Aren't you hungry now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.534: I see...I'd like to eat something.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.535:
Oh, seriously?
Then I'll buy some for Producer too~,chicken~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.536: Which do you prefer, fried or baked?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.537:
That's right...
I'd like it fried.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.538:
Okay, and I'll buy you a cool drink~
Ahaha, mini-cripa~♪
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.539:
...! Sorry...! I'm hungry, but
I don't have time to eat slowly...I still have work to do...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.541: ...I'm sorry for saying something that hurt Mei's feelings...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.542:
...Hmm... Well then! Tell me your plans!
I hope you did it on your free day♪
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.548:
...Maybe you're talking about homework?
I feel like you said that yesterday.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.550: Haha, I can't tell you everything, so next time I'll take notes.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.554:
It was pitch black
When I woke up
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.560: Haha, then it must have been night for me in the distance.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.563: It was floating in the water
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.565:
Ah...I think I saw that program too.
I think it was a broadcast of a pond covered in lotus flowers, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.567: They're not actually floating, they're supported by stems under the water...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.571:
It's floating
but is it supported?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.573:
Ah, Madoka...?
I sent you the materials now, so when I have time...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.574:
Thank you
I have confirmed, there is no problem
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.575:
Oh...have you seen it yet?
Thank you!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.577:
Okay, Madoka confirmed it,
I'll send it to the other party as well!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.582:
Eh, Madoka
Where's the typo...ah...it's cut off...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.583: Last week's photo shoot job was well received
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.585:
The director seems to like Madoka a lot.
I'd love to hear more about him.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.587:
...Madoka is doing a good job.
Thank you so much for everything.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.589:
Hmm? Oh...!
Sorry for calling you so suddenly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.591:
Please tell the director
thank you
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.593:
The sunset is beautiful.
Can you see it Madoka?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.594:
──I can't see
I'm inside the studio
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.596:
If you have a window, take a quick look.
It's a really beautiful sunset.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.601: I don't care that it's beautiful
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.603:
Thank you for your hard work!
I'm heading to the lesson now...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.606: I was at a family restaurant just now...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.607: If we start now, we might be running out of time...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.608:
Okay, thank you
Koito is really serious.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.613:
Ah, um...
Thank you for today!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.614: Haha, what happened all of a sudden?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.616: I wanted to express my gratitude when I can.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.617: Producer-san is there and supports us.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.621:
No, I'm sorry...!
I could feel Koito's seriousness.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.622:
It's not obvious...
That's right, thank you
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.625:
Haha...
After working out a lot in Lesson
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.626:
Yeah...
I'm going to eat something sweet and go home.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.627:
...That's right~!
Producer should go with us~!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.631:
I appreciate your invitation, but
I have some urgent work to do.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.632:
Ah, I guess I can't help it.
I'm going alone with Hinana today.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.633:
Okay, please invite me again
I'll definitely make time and go.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.636:
Thank you for your hard work
It looks like it went well
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.637:
Yeah!
It was so much fun!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.638: I wish Producer could have come too.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.639:
Yeah, sorry
My schedule doesn't work out
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.640:
But you don't have to look to know
Hinana was making everyone happy.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.642:
Even if you're not there, can you understand
Hinana?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.643:
Haha, I know, or maybe I'm just imagining it.
If Hinana is here, I'm sure it will happen.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.647:
Ah...!
Thank you for your hard work at the late lesson
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.654:
...or rather,
It's all of a sudden...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.655:
Yeah...
You sounded a little out of sorts, voice.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.656:
…………
If you don't have anything to do, I'll hang up.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.657:
Hey, thank you for your hard work
What's wrong, Nichika
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.660:
────Melon pudding...!
Have you eaten the one that came out the other day...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.662:
I'm surprised that it's not a melon at all...!
I wonder if they're doing a proper tasting meeting...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.663:
I-I see.
I'll try it next time.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.665:
…………Nichika...
Um...I guess you had something to do?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.668:
Mr. Producer
Are you interested in concept cafes?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.670: Look, the costume you showed me the other day is a sweet loli, or something like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.671: I think that type of conference cafe would be helpful for dressing and movement.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.672:
Ah, I see
I'd be interested in that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.673: Okay, I'll make a reservation for two people.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.675: Oh, maybe another store is better?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.677: Could you please send me the store link later?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.678:
The interior, the atmosphere...
And the price...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.679:
Sorry, I didn't notice the call.
Were you busy with something?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.680:
No, I was just wondering how Self Lesson was going.
You seemed to be pretty focused.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.682:
That would be nice
It was my fault for interfering.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.683: It's okay, I'm not getting in the way
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.684:
I was thinking
it's time to break up...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.690:
There are no Lesson rooms available yet
I have time to wait.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.691: I don't have anything special to do...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.693:
I don't think 
Mikoto's calls are a nuisance.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.696: I never want to call someone like this
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.697:
Haha, isn't that fine?
If you don't mind me, I'll be your one to talk to.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.699:
Producer, may I have a moment?
I'm talking about today's performance...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.700: Huh? Ah, today is the usual ballet performance day.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.701:
Yes
The ticket that Producer gave me
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.702: I thought it might be like work, so I came here.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.703: Well, I guess it's a theater now
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.704:
Yeah...are you glad?
I got this ticket.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.705:
Ah. It was originally given to me by someone at the agency
from a customer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.706: I thought Mikoto would absorb a lot of things.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.710:
Oh, thank you for your hard work
──uh...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.712:
...Is there anything you would like to support?
You're having trouble...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.715:
Even if there was,
I wouldn't provide any support──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.717: If you don't need it, cut it
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.718:
Hey──
I'd like to ask for a photo shoot starting next month...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.721: Maybe it's off-time for extended filming?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.723:
──Haha, I see! Thank you!
Thanks for the great job Luca!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.725: I thought this job would definitely suit Luca, so I'll ask them for more details!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.726:
Luca, you did a great job
Thank you for your hard work
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.730:
Luca?
I was just about to call you too
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.732: Thank you for checking it right away...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.733:
The galley of the live report came up the other day...
Is there anything you're dissatisfied with?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.735: I...I didn't feel comfortable with the words used to introduce Luca, so I'm going to support you there...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.737:
If you don't know
just say it from the beginning.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.738:
Oh, sorry
I'm going to call Luca now...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.741:
Hey, Hana. Thank you for your hard work
Did today's work go well?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.743: I was tired, so I called Producer to try and comfort him.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.744: ...hehe, so I'm glad that Producer answered the phone.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.745:
Haha...!
If you can heal me with just a phone call, that would be the best thing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.747:
...As a reward,
Will you praise me for my hard work?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.749:
──Hana, you did a great job!
I'm looking forward to working hard with you starting tomorrow...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.750:
Hehe, thank you──!
I'll do my best at Work tomorrow as well.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.751: Producer, thank you for your hard work
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.752: Thank you for your hard work, Hana
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.755:
Ah──!
My business...Aha, I wonder what it is
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.756: I wanted to hear the Producer's voice, so I called without thinking.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.758:
...But if you make a long phone call,
you'll get in the way of the Producer, so...I think it's time to hang up, okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.759:
Keep up the good work in the future
Bye
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.762:
Aha, then
Do you feel like eating something sweet right now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.763:
Is it something sweet...?
Yes, I'd be happy if I could eat it...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.765:
Today at the job site,
I was given a piece of cake.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.766: I don't think I can eat it all by myself, so I thought I'd bring it to the office now!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.767:
Oh...!
Sorry for the trouble, thank you
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.770:
──Ah, it's already taken so long...
I'm sorry, it took so long...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.771:
No, it's okay.
It hasn't been that long.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.773:
But, it's really helpful
for you to listen to me like this...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.774: Talking to Producer helped me organize my mind...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.775: I get ideas about what I want to do and feel motivated.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.776:
Haha, I'm glad
But that's Haruki's original power rather than mine.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.778:
It's all thanks to Producer
Because he gives form to what's inside me...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.779: Hehe, please listen to me like this again, okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.780: Producer-san is good at work and kind...it's amazing.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.782:
Hehe~
I can't help it. I always think that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.783:
Haha...
That's nice, but...I'm still a long way off.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.784: There are times when I fail and get lost.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.785: I see...but that's part of what Producer is now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.786: Thanks to that, I'm getting a lot of help right now...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.787: I hope someday...I can become strong enough to help Producer.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.789: Hehe... it seems like there's still a long way to go, but I hope there's a future like that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.791:
Hey, thank you for your hard work
──Haruki, did something good happen?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.792:
Hehe, do you understand?
Actually, I received a stuffed animal as a gift.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.793:
Huh...! Is that so?
What kind of stuffed animal is it?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.794:
It's a sheep
Because it kind of looks like me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.795:
So fluffy and cute...!
I wonder if this is what I feel...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.796: Haha, I'd love to see that
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.797:
Then I'll bring it next time...!
I'll ask Producer to give me a name.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.798:
──You look like Haruki, right?
Then you might want to call me 'Haruki'.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.799:
Hehehe... I'm sure~
But please choose someone other than Haruki-chan~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.800:
Tomorrow's shoot is quite early, but...
Does it look okay?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.802: Well, sometimes I wake up early and prepare for class...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.803:
I'll make sure to set a backup alarm...!
So, it's okay...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.804:
Don't push yourself too hard. Ah, that's right...
I'll give you a wake-up call if you need it────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.805: I-I can't take care of you that much...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.806:
I-I'll wake up by myself!
I'm working...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.807:
...I see, I understand
Then please rest early today and prepare for tomorrow.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.808: Yes...! P,Producer-san, please don't push yourself too hard...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.809:
Haha, that's right. Thank you
I'll make sure you don't oversleep.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.810:
Hey, Producer
Did you see the photo I sent you earlier?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.811:
Hey, you're arranging your hair.
You did a great job with the hairpin.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.812: Today I wore one bun and added various hairpins. Isn't it cute?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.813:
Did you do that yourself?
You tied it up beautifully.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.814:
I was able to do it after watching the videos.
It was fun to see all the different arrangements.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.815:
I see
Hinana is good at arranging hair.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.816:
Wow, that's a compliment!
Now I'm going to paint my nails to match the hairpin.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.817:
I'll send you another photo after I paint it~
Oh, can I give it to Twista~?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.818:
Oh, it's okay
...Hinana is so eager to learn. I'm impressed.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.819:
Hey~~~
Hinana is just doing what she likes~
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.820:
...I see. That's right.
I'm looking forward to the photos.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.822:
Dear Producer...
I would like to ask you something...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.824:
So...
Would you like a wish...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.825:
If you don't mind...
Rinze can make a wish on your behalf...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.826:
A wish...
Of course I have a wish──
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.827: I think I'd like Rinze to make that happen instead of God.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.829: Oh, I want Rinze to continue to be active as an idol.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.831:
Yes...
Rinze will definitely make it happen...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.832:
Hello, Producer?
Sorry, I couldn't answer your call earlier────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.833:
No, it's my fault for calling so suddenly
It's not a big deal...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.834:
You went to New Year's visit the other day, right?
I was just passing by that shrine.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.835: Ah... so you remembered me and called me?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.836:
That's it
So, it's not like I really had anything to do with it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.837: That's a shame...I was really hoping you'd invite me for tea, but...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.838:
Huh? Ah... then, would you like to have some tea?
I just have time before my next job────
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.839:
Oh, that's a boring way to say it
Is that what you say when you ask a lady out?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.840:
Ah, I'm sorry...! That's right... uh...
If you don't mind, would you join me for tea?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.841:
I wanted to have a leisurely chat with Sakuya
about my future work and other things...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.842:
Hehe, I guess it's about work... It seems like you're a producer
Well then... I guess I'll ask you to escort me again.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.843:
Hey,
The party you're invited to starts in the evening, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.844: Hey, I hear you can rent a dress and do some makeup.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.845:
What about Meguru?
Should I ask him?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.846:
I'd like to order both
I don't know which one would be better...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.847:
Please give me everything from top to bottom! I want to do it! 
Your makeup will be 100 times more beautiful than doing it yourself!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.849:
Oh, you thought I was exaggerating
I'm not really good at it, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.850:
You've been invited,
I have to make sure you're clean!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.852:
Right?
I'm going as a 283 professional Hachinomiya Meguru.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.853: I'm going to make sure it's all set up perfectly!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.854:
Isn't there a check on the one you took the other day?
I'm going to the office now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.855:
Thank you
I'm watching it now and it's really good
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.856:
Huh... that's right
I want to see it soon.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.857:
Ah, you'll be surprised
It's cool and cute.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.859:
I tried my best to make the costume look cool, but...
And being cute doesn't go hand in hand...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.860:
That's not true.
The great thing about Juri is that you can balance that.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.861:
Hmm...
I feel a little itchy...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.862: Well...I'm glad it looks like me.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.868: This is a snow rabbit made by Producer!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.870:
You built it next to Yuika-chan's Snow Rabbit,
so we don't have to feel lonely.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.872:
You're welcome
... ah, that. Is it okay to be my Yuki Usagi-san...?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.874:
Thank you for calling.
I'm glad how you feel.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.876:
Hello, Amana
Thank you for your hard work
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.877:
Thank you for your hard work!
Producer...no, Master☆
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.878: Haha, this is a continuation of your previous work, right?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.879:
Yes!
Do you need any help?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.881:
Yeah, I just cleaned up my desk,
I feel like there's more I can do.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.882:
If you don't mind,
could you give me your opinion next time?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.884:
We will definitely live up to your expectations!
Leave it to Amana!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.885: Thank you, I'm looking forward to it
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.887:
It seems like the song program I appeared on the other day
was well received by the viewers.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.888:
Luca's hard work
led to a good result...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.890: Is that why you called me?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.891:
Ah, ah...
I'm sorry, I guess that was unnecessary.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.892: But I wanted to let you know that Luca's hard work is appreciated
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.893: At this rate, I'll do my next job...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.899:
Um... 
The cherry blossoms... are blooming...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.900:
Producer-san...
Sakura...I'm looking forward to it...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.901:
Haha...Yeah, I was looking forward to it.
That's great news.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.906:
Yeah. I'm nearby too.
Can I go over there now?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.911:
...Are you okay?
Please talk to me slowly.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.912:
Tenka, where I went with Producer...
I really wanted to go...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.914:
Okay, I'll be right there
Is there anything noticeable nearby?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.915:
Um, um...
...... there's a narrow road... there's a big tree next to it...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.916:
...Okay, I'm staying somewhere as popular as possible
If you see anything that stands out, please let me know.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.918:
Producer-san! Thank you for your hard work!
I saw the costume!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.919:
Whoa, you're so quick!
I just sent you the materials.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.920: Hey, I want to see it soon...
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.921:
It comes in various colors and looks strong!
The candy cane also looks like a hero...!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.922:
Ah...!
It's like a magic wand
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.923:
Yes
It looks like you can do anything if you shake your head!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.924: I want to wear it soon
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.926: I'm looking forward to seeing Kaho singing and dancing while holding a candy cane.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.927: I'll cast a funny spell on the producer!
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.928:
Thank you for your hard work
The recording finished without any problems.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.929:
Ah, thank you for your hard work
I guess you're going back to the office now.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.931:
Umm...
I got another marshmallow...do you want one?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.932: I appreciate the sentiment, but isn't that what Nichika got?
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.933:
It's okay because I've already eaten
I'm counting the calories.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.934:
I see, it's a shame
I wanted to see Nichika's face as she eats the marshmallow.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.935:
I think it's better to just stop.
That's how you say it.
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallText.937:
I'm glad you called.
I might have punched you if you were right in front of me.

mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.7: This moment is the best time
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.19: The person who gave me something sweet
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.44: I want to know what's inside
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.48: Even if it's an invisible wound
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.49: It doesn't matter how many times it happens
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.73: That's all I want right now
mlPhoneText_PhoneCallTitle.89: One two three with a candy cane

mlProduce_TutorialText.1:
You can do the Lesson while displaying the Tutorial.
Do you want to display the Tutorial?
mlProduce_TutorialText.2: Swipe up to use Produce Card
mlProduce_TutorialText.4: Let's try to complete the game.
mlProduce_TutorialText.5: Swipe left to use Idol Skill.
mlProduce_TutorialText.6: Recover your mental health with Refresh
mlProduce_TutorialText.7: Use Sparkle Sunshine to reduce the required PP for the next card less
mlProduce_TutorialText.9: Continuously use cards with reduced required PP
mlProduce_TutorialText.10: Use Visual Appeal preparation to enhance the following cards
mlProduce_TutorialText.12: Pinch state occurs below 30% of Total Me.
mlProduce_TutorialText.14: Use the immortal melody that resonates in the pinch state
mlProduce_TutorialText.16: Do you want to exit the tutorial?
mlProduce_TutorialText.17: Use hidden in the sea to increase evasion rate
mlProduce_TutorialText.18: Escape probability is displayed above the mental gauge
mlProduce_TutorialText.19: Use sea and singing voice linked to evasion
mlProduce_TutorialText.20: Use ripples and dancing linked to evasion
mlProduce_TutorialText.21: Evasion buff is activated in conjunction with evasion
mlProduce_TutorialText.22: When Me is 80% or higher, it becomes a Safe-state and the number of Appeal points earned increases.
mlProduce_TutorialText.23: In Safe-state, you will receive 20% damage when appealing point in system
mlProduce_TutorialText.25: In Me100% state, you will maintain Safe-state only once even if you receive disadvantages.
mlProduce_TutorialText.26: Use Happy and Dance in Safe-state
mlProduce_TutorialText.27: Recover Me after demerit and transition to Safe-state again.
mlProduce_TutorialText.28:
Currently in Nichika's Phase
Use change to sky to Phase change to Mikoto's Phase
mlProduce_TutorialText.29: Since it's Mikoto's Phase, the Double card has been changed to Mikoto
mlProduce_TutorialText.30: Use the change rank up boost with straddle go up
mlProduce_TutorialText.31: Use change to sky to change phase.
mlProduce_TutorialText.33: You can use Antinomy no Lie to banish cards from your hand
mlProduce_TutorialText.34: The effect is effective when the last song is excluded
mlProduce_TutorialText.35: Let's use the antinomy lie to rule it out
mlProduce_TutorialText.36: It was effective because the last part of the song was excluded
mlProduce_TutorialText.37: When you exclude a card, the number of excluded cards will be added
mlProduce_TutorialText.38: Since the card was deleted, the number of removed cards will be added
mlProduce_TutorialText.39: Use cards and skills to obtain the counter of the corresponding system
mlProduce_TutorialText.40:
By using the Vo card [Vocal Preparation],
Vo counter increased by 1
mlProduce_TutorialText.41: There are also cards with effects that acquire system counters
mlProduce_TutorialText.42: Use [Illusion VOICE], which has the additional effect of [release]
mlProduce_TutorialText.43:
Vo counter was released (consumed)
A lot of Appeal increased by the additional effect
mlProduce_TutorialText.44: Use happiness rhythm with yellow effect that meets the conditions
mlProduce_TutorialText.47:
Use searched powerful rhythms to increase
Max cards in hand
mlProduce_TutorialText.49: Use consult to return the removed card to the Deck
mlProduce_TutorialText.50: Since the card was returned to the deck, the number of removed cards will be subtracted
mlProduce_TutorialText.51: Tap Produce Card to check the effect
mlProduce_TutorialText.52: Produce Cards that glow green can be used
mlProduce_TutorialText.53:
You can check the status of the currently active effect
Tap to display the effect explanation
mlProduce_TutorialText.54: Tap anything other than the card to make it disappear
mlProduce_TutorialText.55: Tap anything other than the icon to make it disappear.

mlProduceKeyword_Description.1: Reduce Me by the value of Mental Guard Reduce the value of Mental Guard by the number of Me reduced (when Me is reduced by the effect of a card used by the player, it cannot be reduced by Mental Guard).
mlProduceKeyword_Description.2: 【Exclusive to L'antica】 Me less than 30% of Max Me
mlProduceKeyword_Description.3: When evasion occurs, the evasion effect disappears and the probability is reset.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.4: The effect is triggered once when evasion occurs.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.5: 【Exclusive to ALSTROEMERIA】 If the unit's Me is 80% or more, Appeal is increased by 10%; if the unit's Me is 90% or more, Appeal is increased by 20% instead; if the unit's Me is 100% or more, Appeal is increased by 40%; if Appeal is increased while the unit is safe, 20% of its Me value is damaged When Appeal is increased in safe state, 20% of Me value is damaged.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.6: Activate the effect when there are more than a certain number of card lines (this card itself is also included in the effect activation conditions).
mlProduceKeyword_Description.7: Add the specified card from the deck to your hand (If the specified card does not exist in the deck, draw a card regardless of the effect)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.8: The specified lineage is added to the card. (When a card with the lineage added is used, the effect is lost. The same lineage cannot be granted)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.9: During Lesson /Special Lesson /Audition, the effect will continue to work.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.10: Additional effects that take effect by consuming a specified number of lineage counters. When there are effects that consume multiple counters of the same lineage, the effect that consumes the most counters takes priority.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.11: Add a card with the same name as the target card to your hand or deck (The rank of the card added by this effect becomes the same as the rank of the duplicated card.)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.12: Removed from the Deck during the game and cannot be added to the hand by drawing cards.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.13: 【Exclusive to SHHis】 If in Nichika Phase, switches to Mikoto Phase / If in Mikoto Phase, switches to Nichika Phase
mlProduceKeyword_Description.14: 【Exclusive to SHHis】 Each time the Phase changes, the rank of the card in hand is increased by one (using a card whose rank is increased by this effect eliminates the change rank boost effect of all cards. It rises to rank 3)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.15: Cards that switch available effects depending on Phase
mlProduceKeyword_Description.16: Effect of reducing your unit's Me by Produce Card or Idol Skill used by you.
mlProduceKeyword_Description.17: Each time a card with a lineage is used, a counter for that lineage is gained (up to 99 counters can be accumulated for each lineage)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.18: PP becomes 0 and cards cannot be used for a certain period of time / The number of seconds of mental break state becomes longer according to the number of mental breaks (Recover from mental break after a certain period of time and return with 50% of Me).
mlProduceKeyword_Description.19: 【Exclusive to CoMETIK】 Increases the number of removed cards by a specified number (the number of removed cards increased by this effect is not decreased)
mlProduceKeyword_Description.20: When the bundle of cards you use is less than the Max number of cards in your hand, the cards after use are added to the Deck, except for the removed cards that are subtracted from the Deck.

mlProduceKeyword_Name.19: Boost in number of cards removed

mlSpecialMission_Empty.1: It will be unlocked when {0} is cleared.

mlSpecialMission_Hint.1: Choose your favorite song and difficulty level from the Live's song selection. Any format of live performance will be counted as a live performance, including normal live performance, auto live performance, skip live performance, and manual play.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.2: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection and press the [Decide] button to start producing. Select a Lesson from the Schedule selection, and win the mini-game in the Lesson.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.3: Pull one Gacha of your choice. Consume a Gacha Ticket or Prism Jewel.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.4: P. Choose a P-idol from the Idol Training screen and raise its Awakening Lv. Awakening Book and Money are required. The required items can be obtained through live performances and producing.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.5: Select the S-character you wish to train from the Support Character building screen and train to increase the Support Characters Lv. Training tickets and Money are required. The required items can be acquired through live performances and productions.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.6: The number of remaining Skip Lives will be reset at midnight every day.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.7: You can start the auto-live by turning on the auto-live function in the unit confirmation after selecting a song. Auto Live is not recorded as a live performance, but you will be rewarded as ALL PERFECT. The number of remaining auto lives will be reset at 0:00 every day.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.8:
After selecting a song, press the LB consumption setting button in the unit confirmation to set the number of LB consumption x 2 or more to start the live performance.

The number of drawings for live rewards after the end of the event will increase according to the number of LBs consumed. Also, the number of plays will be counted together according to the number of LBs consumed.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.9:
After selecting a song, select one of the Idol members in the unit confirmation to change members.

You can also change the composition by clicking on the [Optional Formation] button on the unit checklist.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.10: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection screen and press the [Decide] button to start producing. Select an Audition that will be held in the last week of the month from the schedule selection screen, and win the mini-game in the Audition.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.11: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection screen, press the [Decide] button to start producing, and play to the end.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.12: Select one of the units from the Produce Episode selection screen, press the [Decide] button, select an Idol from the Produce Select Idol screen, select an Idol other than the one currently displayed as [Establishment], and press the [Decide] button in the lower right corner of the screen to organize the Idol. Press the decision button in the lower right corner of the screen to organize the unit.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.13: Exchange any item from the exchange. The items to be exchanged differ depending on the tab. Mainly, Money, Rainbow Rocks, Star Shards, and Season Medals are consumed.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.14: Select [Search Friends] from the [Friends] screen, select any friend and press the [Follow] button.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.15: Set the Birthday from the Producer Information profile screen.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.16: Select the Friend Support Characters icon from the Producer Information profile screen and set up any Friend Support Characters.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.17: From the Producer Information profile screen, click on the Comments column and edit any comment you wish.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.18: Click the [Favorite Idol] button on the lower left of the Producer Information profile screen, select the desired Produce Idol, and click the [Change] button.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.19: From the Producer Information profile screen, click on the [Unset] column for the title, select any title, and change it.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.20: Select illumination STARS from the main tab of the story, then select Chapter 1 to read the story.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.21: Press the Idol tab of the story and select any Idol, then select Chapter 1 to read the story.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.22: Press the third icon from the upper right corner of the home screen, select the Idol you have set up, and then select any Idol from the Idol settings. The selected Idol will appear in front of the left side of the desk.
mlSpecialMission_Hint.23:
Stage Costumes can be changed from the costume icon in the costume tab of the live unit selection screen.

Stage Costume cannot be changed for P-idol before producing. F-Idol after produce can be changed in unit setup.

mlStore_ItemCaveat.9:
・Even if you have purchased a Season Pass, you will not be able to receive the Premium Rewards for any Season Rank that you have not yet achieved.
・Season Pass can be purchased until 23:59 11/28/2023, but the Season Pass effect will last until 23:59 11/30/2023.
・The Season Pass effect will be inherited even if the model is changed to another OS.
・The Season Pass effect is inherited when playing multi-session play with other devices.
・Season Pass is not available for payment at shop from the time of purchase until the payment is completed.
・Season Pass cannot be returned or exchanged at any time.
mlStore_ItemCaveat.10:
・This product may be purchased up to one time.
・Private can be worn in the story and on the home screen. It cannot be set as a Stage Costume and cannot be worn in a live performance.
・If you already own any of the costumes, hairstyles or accessories included in this product, you will not be able to acquire those costumes, hairstyles or accessories.
・【Costume 02】 Saijo Juri may be obtained at a later date at a different location. Please understand this in advance.
mlStore_ItemCaveat.11:
・Login Bonus Pass holders will receive 100 Prism Jewels once a day when they log in to the game.
・The opportunity to receive Prism Jewel is reset at 0:00 every day.
・If you have logged in for 25 days or more within 30 days of purchasing your Login Bonus Pass, you will receive a total of 2500 Prism Jewels.
・If you have not logged in for less than 24 days within 30 days of purchasing your Login Bonus Pass, you will lose the Prism Jewel you have not received.
・Prism Jewel will be sent to your Gift Box.
・If you change your device to another operating system, your Login Bonus Pass will be transferred to the new device.
・Login Bonus Pass will be inherited even when playing multi-session play with other devices.
・Prism Jewel obtained by Login Bonus Pass is free Prism Jewel. The free Prism Jewel cannot be used for the paid Prism Jewel service.
・The Login Bonus Pass will not be effective until the payment is completed after the purchase of the product.
・Login Bonus Pass cannot be returned or exchanged at any time.

mlTips_Description.1: Enjoy the story and develop your Idol while strengthening your status and Produce Cards, and aim to pass the Auditions.
mlTips_Description.2: They are used in Lessons and Auditions. Collect Produce Cards that have various effects to give your idols an advantage.
mlTips_Description.3: By selecting a Produce Policy, the selected effect will be applied during the Season.
mlTips_Description.4: Depending on each schedule, you can increase your status and obtain Produce Cards. Stamina is consumed depending on the type of schedule.
mlTips_Description.5: The goal is to maximize Appeal Points within the time limit by making full use of Produce Cards.
mlTips_Description.6: The goal is to maximize Appeal Points before your Rival does within the time limit. By surpassing the time limit, you can advance to the next Season.
mlTips_Description.7: Tap the heart mark on the song jacket to register/unregister Favorite songs. Registering frequently played songs makes it easier to find songs.
mlTips_Description.8: By playing various songs, [Overall High Score Rate] and [Overall Technical Rate] will increase and rate frames and rewards will be earned.
mlTips_Description.9: This is the total High Score Rate of the top 20 songs recorded by manual play, and you can aim for a new High Score by increasing the Total Stats.
mlTips_Description.10: This is the average of the Technical Rate of the top 20 scores recorded in manual play. Technical score is calculated based on the judgment result only.
mlTips_Description.11: When there's a song that cannot be cleared, try to form units with Life Recovery or Invincibility and fans boosting skills when you want to increase fans.
mlTips_Description.12: Once you complete a produce run and acquire Fes Idols, you will get one Live Skill. P.idols who have not yet produced will not acquire any Live Skill.
mlTips_Description.13: Idols marked [CENTER] and [ONSTAGE] will appear on the stage. When multiple Idols of the same name are organized, other Idols will appear randomly.
mlTips_Description.14: When organized as the center of a live unit, the Live Skill can be activated up to twice, doubling the EXP gained and the No. of fans after the live performance.
mlTips_Description.15: If you set-up Idols with the same type mark as the song, the unit bonus will be added and the Total Stats will be increased. You can check the bonus in the Unit Set-up screen.
mlTips_Description.16: Each P-idol has a unique Costume. By training to 3★, Stage Costume will be unlocked, and the costumes can be changed during live performances.
mlTips_Description.17: Money can be used to exchange items used for awakening and training at the exchange.
mlTips_Description.18: Expired exchange points become Star Shards. You can exchange Star Shards for other items at the exchange.
mlTips_Description.19: An item used for Idol Skill LvUp of Produce Idol.
mlTips_Description.20: The item used to awaken the Produce Idol. There are common awakening books and individual awakening books for each unit.
mlTips_Description.21: You can exchange Rainbow Rocks for pieces at the exchange.
mlTips_Description.22: Items that can be used to Recover ST (Stamina).
mlTips_Description.23: Items that can be used to Recover LB (Live Boost).
mlTips_Description.24: Items that can be acquired at various points in the game and may be used in gachas, stores, ST Recovery, LB Recovery, etc.
mlTips_Description.25: Items used for special training of Produce Idol and master training of Support Characters.
mlTips_Description.26: Items used for training of Support Characters.
mlTips_Description.27: The Season Mission is held for a certain period of time, and you can play the Season Mission and earn rewards for completing the Season Mission.
mlTips_Description.28: This is where you can exchange one item for another. You can exchange Money, Star Shards, Rainbow Rocks, Season Medals, etc. for another item.
mlTips_Description.29: You can change settings for the entire application from the menu in the upper right corner of the home screen.
